OL,3,C80% of 85 to 95-year-olds now pay with
OL,4,Ccontactless, says Barclays
OL,6,FFor the second year running, the
OL,7,FFriday just before Christmas (December
OL,8,F22 2023) was the single biggest day
OL,9,Ffor contactless payments, as shoppers
OL,10,Fpicked up last-minute gifts, or
OL,11,Fenjoyed a few drinks with friends as
OL,12,Fthey clocked off for their festive
OL,13,Fbreak.
OL,15,FWhile contactless is still more
OL,16,Fpopular among younger generations, the
OL,17,Fgap between older and younger people
OL,18,Fis continuing to narrow, Barclays said.
