OL,3,C80% of 85 to 95-year-olds now pay with
OL,4,Ccontactless, says Barclays
OL,6,FIn 2023, the proportion of active
OL,7,Fusers among 85 to 95-year-olds (80.1%)
OL,8,Fpassed 80% for the first time.
OL,10,FAnd for the third year in a row, the
OL,11,Fover-65s were the fastest-growing
OL,12,Fgroup for contactless usage, Barclays
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FA survey of 2,000 people by Opinium
OL,16,FResearch for Barclays indicated just
OL,17,F3% of over-75s prefer using mobile
OL,18,Fpayments to physical cards ` compared
OL,19,Fwith a quarter (25%) of 18 to 34-year-
OL,20,Folds who said they prefer to use their
OL,21,Fphone.
